    "SRS provides efficient search results with a relatively small index size, while QALSH enhances bucketing precision by using the incoming query as a reference point.",
    "The 𝛿-𝜖-approximate search accuracy/efficiency tradeoff is tuned with user-defined parameters that specify the approximation error and probability thresholds.",
